Package provided.jxMaps.utils

Supplied utilities to help manage the JxMaps library.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAction<T>
    A synonym for Consumer<T> that helps convey the semantic of an action based on an input of type T.
    IBiAction<T,​U>
    A synonym for BiConsumer<T, U> that helps convey the semantic of an action based on two inputs of types T and U.
    IDistanceCases
    An interface that supplies cases for distance-related operations.
    IJxMaps_Defs
    A collection of JxMaps-related definitions
    IJxMaps_Defs.IEvent
    Nested interface to hold definitions for events.
    IJxMapsComponentsFactory
    A factory that encapsulates the generation of entities that bound to an associated Map object.
    IMapLayer
    A Set of MapObjects that can be treated as a whole
    IMapNavigator
    An encapsulation of the movement and event-based actions of an associated map.
    IOptionedMapObject<TOptions>
    Interface that represents a MapObject whose configuration options be both get and set.
    IPlace
    Represents a named location on a map with an associated default zoom level when viewing it.
    IVisibleMapObject
    A MapObject that has a notion of visibility
